## Checklist

### Sprint Ready
- [ ] Are KRs quantified? (Number + unit)
- [ ] Are tasks broken down? (2-day or smaller units)
- [ ] Are dependencies identified?
- [ ] Are owners assigned?
- [ ] Are risks identified?

### Handoff Ready
- [ ] Is the spec document complete?
- [ ] Is the design finalized?
- [ ] Is event logging defined?
- [ ] Is the Definition of Done (DoD) clear?
- [ ] Are answers to dev team questions prepared?

### Retrospective Ready
- [ ] Are KR achievement results compiled?
- [ ] Are wins documented?
- [ ] Are areas for improvement documented?
- [ ] Are next actions derived?

